    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car enthusiasts! It truly tugs at my heartstrings to post this, but the time has come for my pride and joy to find a new garage. I\u2019ve treated this beauty like a member of the family\u2014always hand-washed, garage-kept, and maintained with an open checkbook. It\u2019s in such incredible shape that you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor. Aside from a tiny, almost invisible mark on the wheel that only a perfectionist like me would notice, it\u2019s absolutely flawless. It drives like a dream and smells like new. I\u2019d love for you to come by, have a coffee, and see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of this car!",
      "price": 48500.0,
